 :tx/rationale "Create task: CE-1: MaterializedViews struct — incremental F(S) accumulators as Store field (INV-BILATERAL-001 L1, INV-BILATERAL-002, ADR-COHERENCE-003). BACKGROUND: F(S) has 7 components currently computed by 7 separate functions doing full O(n) scans. Each component can be maintained as a running accumulator updated in O(1) per datom. The spec (INV-BILATERAL-001 L1) requires F(S) to be monotonically non-decreasing — making it a Store field makes this structurally verifiable. APPROACH: (1) Define MaterializedViews struct with 7 accumulators: validation_map: HashMap<EntityId,i64> (spec->max_verification_depth), coverage_set: HashSet<EntityId> (impl target specs), namespace_counts: (usize,usize,usize) (intent/spec/impl datom counts for drift), methodology_counters: (tx_count,observation_count,harvest_count etc for M(t)), conflict_index: HashMap<(EntityId,Attribute),BTreeMap<TxId,Vec<Value>>> (for contradiction detection), completeness_map: HashMap<EntityId,(bool,bool)> (has_impl,has_task per spec), uncertainty_accum: (f64,usize) (sum_confidence,count for running average). (2) Add spec_element_set: HashSet<EntityId> for tracking which entities are spec elements. (3) Add task_counts: (open,in_progress,closed,blocked) maintained incrementally. (4) Add fn observe(&mut self, datom: &Datom, schema: &Schema) that classifies each datom by attribute and updates the relevant accumulators. (5) Add fn fitness(&self) -> FitnessScore that computes F(S) from accumulators in O(1). (6) Add fn coherence(&self) -> CoherenceReport that computes Phi, beta_1 from namespace_counts in O(1). (7) Derive Serialize, Deserialize on MaterializedViews (included in store.bin). (8) Add views: MaterializedViews field to Store struct. ACCEPTANCE: (A) MaterializedViews::fitness() matches compute_fitness() to within 1e-10 for any store state. (B) MaterializedViews::coherence() matches check_coherence_fast() for Phi and live projection counts. (C) views field serialized in store.bin (verified by round-trip). (D) observe() is O(1) per datom (no store-wide scans). (E) Task counts from views match task_counts() batch computation. FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/store.rs, crates/braid-kernel/src/bilateral.rs (new views module). TRACES-TO: INV-BILATERAL-001, INV-BILATERAL-002, ADR-COHERENCE-003, ADR-STORE-005."
